OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers may linger initially, but
OL,7,Fslowly fading through the evening to
OL,8,Fgive a mostly dry and fine night with
OL,9,Fsome clear spells developing. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FWednesday generally dry and
OL,13,Fbright, with some sunny spells likely
OL,14,Facross the region. Light winds
OL,15,Ffreshening a little in afternoon.
OL,16,FPatchy rain possible overnight.
